Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:18.47,edcn,NTP,0,0,12,,{\an8\fs20\1cDC7330\bord0}设施  人才  资金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央种子岛高中机器人研究部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向拥有技术合作关系的JAXA要求这三项资源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一  用于组装机器人的设施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二  熟悉机器人技术的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三  用于研发的资金  最少也要100万
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100万？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  最少也需要这个数字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一分也不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你们的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸要先去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  你是准备趁机开溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是种子岛宇宙中心的所长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总能想出办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是所长但充其量也就是个中层干部而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是听从领导的指示老老实实做事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么说啊  父亲的威严都扫地了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海同学也帮我说两句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Robo部正在制作的Gun制造1号机可不是普通的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是从姐姐那时就开始制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的两个女儿的梦想结晶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…你说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就和你妈妈商量商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能跟妈妈说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个完全不懂梦想和浪漫的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  爸爸你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拥有热情  会义无反顾地去追逐梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢那样的爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚希穗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从现在的爸爸身上  我完全感觉不到热情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果你还拥有着热情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还是我最喜欢的爸爸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了我的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然跑到爸爸的单位要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子里究竟在想些什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好可是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸是很宠你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可不记得有把你教成这么贪财的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失望到差点就想发射Gunvarrel十字火箭拳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为小亚希的要求太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且话说回来  TNSC可是火箭发射基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊  但JAXA不是有一个宇宙机器人技术部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出门之前我就说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你希望得到机器人技术部的协助的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该去东京或者筑波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c0000E0}「嘁  为什么你总是满嘴歪理」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我倒觉得他说的没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  海要帮昴说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我还想让你当Gun制造1号机的机师的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情我坚决不干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？提到机师不都是名人吗  这可是一种荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里光荣了  完全就是个牺牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八汐学长真是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是你的话肯定会一声不吭偷偷溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此  我就使用ROBO-ONE的奖金独力完成它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱是不会打过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没在说小充的工资  而是在说奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小充  我可要报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能独吞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是公办高等中学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奖金会算作明年的活动经费
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说要等到明年4月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像已经毕业了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你没留级的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  濑乃宫妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我妹妹  小充
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是  不要叫我小充
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,118)\fs20\frz19\bord0\shad2}通话结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢  还要付钱给DOKU
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我讨厌你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(415,340)\fs16\frz11}收到了FRAU KOUJIRO发来的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你便了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(178,108)\fs10\frz-20\1c000000\bord0}旧种子岛机场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,165)\fs14\frz-20\1c000000\bord0}请给我到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位置是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是{\1cFF9F00}雷霆王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八汐  你这身打扮是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种时候  要穿就算弄脏了也无所谓的体操服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是小常识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是被人叫过来了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到古郡居然认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古郡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上次去东京的时候认识的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙意外的会勾搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我被骗了啊  我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连忙都不帮就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\fad(150,150)}注：FRAU KOUJIRO在说话时略有口吃\N翻译时为保持简洁一律省略  请大家自行体会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经受不了这个岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是FRAU KOUJIRO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  笔名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  那么古郡是真名？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  古郡可奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她明天起就会转入我们高中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  谁叫那种{\1cFF9F00}DQN{\r}名字啊  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(309,325)\fs16{\1cFF9F00}Tera
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1cFF9F00}兆恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像让人有点搞不懂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  开始吧  八汐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  开始干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是搬家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那个该死的教导主任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我非得帮学生搬家不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬家…  搬到这里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  八汐  过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要拜托我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在「Killballad」里打赢我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于我提供给你程序这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该还我个人情吧{\1cFF9F00}常考
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FRAU炭可没有好人到不求回报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜呼呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去掉驾驶舱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能乘坐怎么能算是巨型机器人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个设计图是10年前的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在遥控才是主流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个外部装饰也应该拆掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那样太丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底这个机器人的重量本身就是个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然想在世博会上展出这种浑身缺陷连走都不能走的机器人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gun制造1号机是历代Robo部员一点一点努力制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它本身就等同于Robo部的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把它拆掉…这我做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  昴说的话  全部驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罢  我只是想尽一下部员的义务而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能…下狠心把它扔掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(40,120)\pos(312,118)\fs18\frz11\bord0\shad2}海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(40,120)\pos(305,159)\fs10\frz11\bord0\shad2}来电
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(40,0)\pos(282,200)\fs14\frz11\bord0\shad2}接听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(40,0)\pos(371,181)\fs14\frz11\bord0\shad2}拒接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,120)\pos(371,181)\fs14\frz11\bord0\shad2}拒接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你状态如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就再给你汇报一个糟糕透顶的消息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我总是在吃的那个「宇宙糖」的公司的社长是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是小充的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到我一直在给长深田一家人送钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真想让他们还一点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来  我们Robo部也就有活动经费可用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你提供的情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是一如既往的精神可嘉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的腿又不灵便了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日常维护而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这件事我必须亲自动手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,325)\fs16{\1cFF9F00}Crash
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是{\1cFF9F00}「15年崩坏」{\r}时开始用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算来这家伙也陪了我4年了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏它努力到了现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它可是美纱姐送的  也不能随便丢掉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了些吃的来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1cFF9F00}言射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么看  她都像个地缚灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Skal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京的话不怎么常见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)\fs16\1cFF9F00}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1cFF9F00}乙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  语言太不通了  {\1cFF9F00}急墙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我这就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天准备请装潢公司来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之安保要放在第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道  我迄今为止所收集的腐图之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经轻松超过1TB了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜呼呼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是那样的话  你买个普通点的房子不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种废墟的感觉才比较萌吧  常考
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后强求穿牛仔裤裸上半身的帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父母呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1cFF9F00}开贴了我就说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1cFF9F00}内裤飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少爸爸在东京
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈她？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上周好像举行了机器人大赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  那已经和我无关了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不玩定制机器人了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Space Ame股份有限公司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充彦你也终于有了这么可爱的学生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上课的时候没有欲火焚身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会对这种黄毛丫头…哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长深田一族真是差劲至极
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  关于我刚才说的那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我们赞助的话  还稍微差点冲击力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲击力？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说是满溢的朝气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是该说「咚」一下的那种感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波霸  波霸  丰乳肥臀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对对  就是那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…  请问…  「波霸」是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:15:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波霸就是指胸部很大的女人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔  你说这话是不是对她有点失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  濑乃宫妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦  这样啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样她会很受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel十字火箭拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八汐学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然会主动搭话还真是罕见啊  Pleiades君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我是有事情找你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个月在拉斯维加斯将会举办第一届ROBO-ONE世界大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被选为了日本代表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八汐学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我联手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我话还没说完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你既没有必要说完  我也不打算听
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你对战之后我确信了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能和学长你联手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能在世界级的舞台上一展拳脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成是个基佬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就明说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实非常讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为操作员的才能又是另外一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要用这么炙热的眼神看着我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就用「Killballad」来一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我赢了  你就得听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说  你怕输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是白费工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你输了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海在「Killballad」上输给他了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我连胜了21场  然后栽在了第22场上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就该限制回合数的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得海像是昴的小弟一样  好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这该算是格斗游戏玩家的尊严吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  我要是赢了也能收海当小弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我觉得小亚希就算挑战我一百次也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你燃起来了也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来昴人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去FRAU那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像对这家伙的操作程序很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FRAU？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像决定在这种子岛上住下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗号？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是和你同班的日高…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请  请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为程序的所有权在她手上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有她的许可的话  也就只能放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那我可不会出场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长你不是说过输了就什么都听我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  海被说得没脾气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个要去参加世界大赛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那段时间的Gun制造工作该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…就算不参赛我也基本不打算帮忙就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…  呜呜  哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Gunvarrel十字火箭拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程序之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须先让学长牢记M45的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都是在守株待兔不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在原地摆好架势  等对手冲过来就将其抓住并扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是不太喜欢这种战术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  为了弥补这种战术攻击距离短的缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(382,325)\fs16}Pile Bunker
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给它装备了打桩机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那种装置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要算准与对手间的距离  再用这种速度发射出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是躲不开的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  不要用名誉部长来做实验啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但八汐学长你却躲开了它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那时的反应速度非比寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是一句「荒谬」就能解释的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能再来一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想破了脑袋都猜不透其中的玄机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那究竟是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我可以肯定那不是什么必杀技
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去看H2火箭发射的那一天后过了4个月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2010年9月11日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(279,325)\fs16}Anemone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了银莲花号集体昏迷事件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为参加了学校组织的轮船观光之旅而登船的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:20:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在从鹿儿岛回来的船上遭遇了这起事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集体昏迷的原因至今仍旧是一个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只有我和小亚希在恢复意识后留下了巨大的后遗症
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一种被称作{\1cFF9F00}「Elephant Mouse症候群」{\r}的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致人产生「慢动作」和「快进」的体感的症状
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会因为学弟的一句话而心头不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是太年轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是TAGIRIN吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(300,322)\fs18\frz-10.5}收到邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(190,68)\fs10\frz-10.5\bord1.5}发信人   GEZI姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GEZI姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是信号不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…能听见吗
